---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Learn" description="Plain-English guides to how U.S. government works, what's on your ballot, and why it matters.">

  <!-- HERO: PAGE HEADER + RIGHT NOW -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pt-16 pb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Learn</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/50 max-w-2xl mb-10">
        Plain-English guides to how U.S. government works, what's on your ballot, and why it matters. No spin&mdash;just the facts.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-white/40 mb-1">Right Now</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-tossup mb-6"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/learn/follow-the-money" class="group block bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-ind bg-ind/15 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">
            Investigation
          </span>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-tossup transition-colors">
            Follow the Money
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4 text-sm">
            How DOGE, the crypto industry, and a $10 billion peace deal trace back to the 2024 election.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-navy/40 text-white/70">DOGE</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-tossup/30 text-tossup">Crypto</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-ind/30 text-ind">Board of Peace</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm text-tossup font-medium group-hover:underline">
            Read the full timeline &rarr;
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/learn/save-act" class="group block bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-tossup bg-tossup/15 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">
            Legislation
          </span>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-tossup transition-colors">
            The SAVE Act, Explained
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4 text-sm">
            What the SAVE America Act would change about voter registration and ID requirements&mdash;and what it means for the 2026 midterms.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3 mb-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-white/40 mb-1">Current Status</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
              <span class="font-semibold text-tossup">Passed House</span> 218&ndash;213<br/>
              Senate vote expected week of Feb 24
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm text-tossup font-medium group-hover:underline">
            Read the full explainer &rarr;
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE BASICS -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-navy mb-1">The Basics</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-dem mb-6"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <a href="/learn/what-are-midterms" class="group block bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-dem mb-2">Start Here</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors mb-2">What Are Midterm Elections?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">What midterm elections are, why they matter, and what's on the ballot.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/how-congress-works" class="group block bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-dem mb-2">Start Here</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors mb-2">How Congress Works</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">The Senate, the House, and how a bill becomes a law.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE BODIES -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-navy mb-1">The Bodies</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-navy mb-6"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a href="/senate" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200 hover:border-navy/40 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-navy/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-navy font-bold text-sm">S</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">The Senate</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">100 members &middot; 6-year terms</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/house" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200 hover:border-navy/40 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-navy/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-navy font-bold text-sm">H</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">The House</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">435 members &middot; 2-year terms</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/governors" class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200 hover:border-navy/40 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-navy/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-navy font-bold text-sm">G</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Governors</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">State executives &middot; 36 races in 2026</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DEEP DIVES -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-navy mb-1">Deep Dives</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-slate-300 mb-8"></div>

      <!-- Sub-group: How Government Works -->
      <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-400 mb-3">How Government Works</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-8">
        <a href="/learn/congressional-hearings" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Congressional Hearings</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">What they are, how they work, and whether they lead to anything.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/executive-orders" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Executive Orders</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">What they are, how they compare to laws, and what Congress can do.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/bills-and-votes" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">How Bills &amp; Votes Work</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">From introduction to the president's desk, plus filibusters and cloture.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/career-ladder" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">The Political Career Ladder</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">How politicians move between the House, Senate, and governor's mansion.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/pacs-and-super-pacs" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">PACs &amp; Super PACs</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Where the money comes from, where it goes, and why it matters.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/follow-the-money" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Follow the Money</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">How DOGE, crypto, and a $10B peace deal trace back to the 2024 election.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Sub-group: Elections & Voting -->
      <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-400 mb-3">Elections &amp; Voting</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        <a href="/learn/reading-your-ballot" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Reading Your Ballot</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">A visual walkthrough of what you'll see when you vote.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/open-closed-primaries" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Open vs. Closed Primaries</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">How your party registration affects whether you can vote in a primary.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/voter-turnout" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Voter Turnout in America</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">How many Americans actually vote, who shows up, and why it matters.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/special-elections" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Special Elections</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">The elections nobody tells you about&mdash;and why so few voters decide them.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/race-ratings" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">Understanding Race Ratings</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">What Safe, Likely, Lean, and Toss-Up mean and who decides.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/learn/after-you-vote" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-dem/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-navy group-hover:text-dem transition-colors">After You Vote</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Ballot tracking, counting, certification, recounts, and runoffs.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GET INVOLVED -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-white/60 mb-1">Get Involved</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-tossup mb-6"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/learn/how-to-run" class="group block bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-white group-hover:text-tossup transition-colors mb-2">How to Run for Congress</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Eligibility, filing, primaries, fundraising, and getting on the ballot.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/take-action" class="group block bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-white group-hover:text-tossup transition-colors mb-2">Take Action</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Register to vote, find your reps, and get involved in your community.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
